critical_positive: My partner was a kind person and helped open up the conversation by talking about his location and asking about mine. He asked questions when things slowed down, I think. critical_negative: I felt that it was kind of dull and that we talked quite a bit about things that I'm tired of talking about. critical_positive: The conversation was just fine. She was very personable and charming, we were able to find things we have in common, politics being the one we spoke about the most.
